00:40:37,710 --> 00:40:39,560
Do you think Yun Hongqi

842
00:40:39,580 --> 00:40:41,580
truly has genuine feelings for you?

843
00:40:41,860 --> 00:40:42,660
You're wrong.

844
00:40:42,990 --> 00:40:45,190
He's been investigating you all along.

845
00:40:45,310 --> 00:40:46,390
He and his family

846
00:40:46,390 --> 00:40:48,070
have never truly trusted you.

847
00:40:48,750 --> 00:40:51,010
When you were taken to the NBIS last time,

848
00:40:51,060 --> 00:40:52,280
