849
00:40:52,690 --> 00:40:53,930
He also knows

850
00:40:54,150 --> 00:40:55,550
that you're being monitored by the NBIS.

851
00:40:55,550 --> 00:40:57,150
If he really cared about you,

852
00:40:57,180 --> 00:40:58,840
he would've found a way to have the NBIS

853
00:40:58,840 --> 00:41:00,500
lift the surveillance on you.

854
00:41:02,180 --> 00:41:03,610
If he really trusted you,

855
00:41:04,210 --> 00:41:06,390
after all the time you've spent with Yun Hongqi,

856
00:41:06,390 --> 00:41:09,590
you would have uncovered Yun Hongshen's every movement.

857
00:41:09,850 --> 00:41:10,910
He might have a tiny bit of feeling

858
00:41:10,910 --> 00:41:12,350
for you,

859
00:41:13,390 --> 00:41:15,390
but those feelings are insignificant,

860
00:41:15,390 --> 00:41:17,120
and they'll fade in an instant.

861
00:41:17,500 --> 00:41:18,940
Because, to them,

862
00:41:19,510 --> 00:41:20,680
you are nothing.

