00:41:53,050 --> 00:41:55,180
despite being carefully calculated—

872
00:41:55,260 --> 00:41:56,830
still left loopholes,

873
00:41:57,260 --> 00:42:00,140
while Ling Han remained flawless.

874
00:42:08,880 --> 00:42:10,540
What loopholes could he have?

875
00:42:10,750 --> 00:42:12,220
He didn't personally kill

876
00:42:12,720 --> 00:42:13,850
Li Miaohan's lover.

877
00:42:14,630 --> 00:42:16,630
Bai Qingkui didn't seem to know him.

878
00:42:16,960 --> 00:42:18,560
Jin Guoqiang's car accident

879
00:42:18,560 --> 00:42:19,820
and even Myna's murder

880
00:42:20,080 --> 00:42:21,610
have nothing to do with him.

881
00:42:22,870 --> 00:42:23,930
What else is there?

882
00:42:31,040 --> 00:42:31,900
The cipher key.

883
00:42:32,700 --> 00:42:34,760
He was the one who took the cipher key.

884
00:42:40,120 --> 00:42:41,350
Good morning, Old Madam.

885
00:42:41,350 --> 00:42:42,150
Good morning.

886
00:42:42,580 --> 00:42:44,630
Where are the Young Master and the Second Young Master?

887
00:42:44,630 --> 00:42:46,590
It seems something happened at the school.

888
00:42:46,590 --> 00:42:48,590
The Young Master left at the crack of dawn,

889
00:42:48,590 --> 00:42:50,090
and the Second Young Master also said he had something to do.

890
00:42:50,090 --> 00:42:52,020
He just rushed out a moment ago.

891
00:42:52,730 --> 00:42:54,390
You see, both of them are busy.

892
00:42:54,410 --> 00:42:55,310
Such a big family,

893
00:42:55,310 --> 00:42:56,680
and it's just the two of us now.
